<p>Using your own domain to direct short URLs with 0tr.me is easy and <strong>free</strong> using Page Rules and some DNS magic! We're<span class="no-mobile"> going to assume you're</span> using Cloudflare<span class="no-mobile"> for this, but most DNS providers have a similar setup and this should work fine with them</span>.</p>

<ol>
  <li>Launch <span class="no-mobile">your</span> <a href="https://dash.cloudflare.com">Cloudflare <span class="no-mobile">Dashboard</span></a> and choose the site you want <span class="no-mobile">to use</span> for <span class="no-mobile">0tr.me</span> short URLs
  <br>
